 119:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c **** /**
 120:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c **** @code  
 121:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  
 122:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  This driver provides functions to configure and program the Flash memory of all STM32F10x devices,
 123:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  including the latest STM32F10x_XL density devices. 
 124:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c **** 
 125:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  STM32F10x_XL devices feature up to 1 Mbyte with dual bank architecture for read-while-write (RWW) 
 126:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****     - bank1: fixed size of 512 Kbytes (256 pages of 2Kbytes each)
 127:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****     - bank2: up to 512 Kbytes (up to 256 pages of 2Kbytes each)
 128:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  While other STM32F10x devices features only one bank with memory up to 512 Kbytes.
 129:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c **** 
 130:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  In version V3.3.0, some functions were updated and new ones were added to support
 131:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  STM32F10x_XL devices. Thus some functions manages all devices, while other are 
 132:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  dedicated for XL devices only.
 133:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  
 134:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****  The table below presents the list of available functions depending on the used STM32F10x devices. 
 135:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****       
 136:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****    ***************************************************
 137:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****    * Legacy functions used for all STM32F10x devices *
 138:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****    ***************************************************
 139:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****    +-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 140:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****    |       Functions prototypes         |STM32F10x_XL|Other STM32F10x|    Comments                 
 141:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****    |                                    |   devices  |  devices      |                             
 142:Drivers/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_flash.c ****    |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
